state legislation allowing health experts to determine appropriate
levels.
</P>
<P>
   Brockovich and her boss, attorney Ed Masry, won a $333 million
lawsuit against Pacific Gas &AMP; Electric on behalf of 650 residents
of the town of Hinkley who claimed the utility contaminated their
water with chromium 6.
</P>
