<HEADLINE> Chelsea Watches Olympic Volleyball  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   SYDNEY, Australia (AP) -- Chelsea Clinton endured the Australian
sun to watch Olympic beach volleyball, taking in parts of two
matches in the women's losers' bracket competition.
</P>
<P>
   Chelsea, wearing a white cotton top and aqua skirt with
