<HEADLINE> Coolmars Wins Breeders Classic  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   CHARLES TOWN, W.Va. (AP) -- Coolmars won the $225,000 West
Virginia Breeders Classic by 1&AMP;frac14; lengths at Charles Town Races on
Sunday.
</P>
<P>
   With jockey Mark Rosenthal aboard, Coolmars covered the 1
1-8-mile track in 1 minute, 54.49 seconds, which was four seconds
slower than last year's record time set by A Huevo.
</P>
