   ''When I hit the wire, I thought it was a dream at first,''
Rosenthal said.
</P>
<P>
   Rebellious Dreamer, the favorite, came in second, followed
closely by Early Package, a 17-1 longshot.
</P>
<P>
   Coolmars returned $13.60, $4 and $4. Owner Neil Glasser had
claimed Coolmars for $10,000 in December.
</P>
